name: "Nefertiti Dreaming 1
description:
“Nefertiti Dreaming”
Alison Williams
Realms to meander eternally. Photographic and digital artworks which evolve into a series of imaginary landscapes. The line between reality and fantasy blurs.  Could you walk here ? Each artwork becomes an individual part of the dream journey. These digital artworks are based on a near-death experience which evolved into thoughts and images of an interpreted Afterlife.
